South Africa’s Eskom to Buy 373 Megawatts of Power From Sasol, Sappi, Ipsa

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-27T11:58:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/south-africa-s-eskom-to-buy-373-megawatts-of-power-from-sasol-sappi-ipsa.html
Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd., South
Africa’s state-owned power utlity, said it signed agreements to
buy 373 megawatts of electricity from companies including  Sasol
Ltd. (SOL) ,  Sappi Ltd. (SAP)  and  Ipsa Group Plc. (IPSA)   Eskom commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  